                            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                                                <h1 class="main-title-bg">&nbsp;Synergy API Connector offer<br></h1>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li class="p-2"><strong>Pull API data to Google Sheets</strong><br>APIs are used by thousands of websites to enable access to their platforms. API Connector allows you to pull data from these APIs right into your Google Sheets worksheet without having to write any code.<br></li>
